   Frequently Asked Questions

   Skip Telephone FAQ Links Telephone
     * What is the Subscriber Line Charge and why do I have to pay this
       charge?
     * What is the Universal Service Fund or Universal Connectivity Charge
       and why do I have to pay this charge?
     * What is slamming and what can I do about it?
     * How do I stop telemarketing calls to my home?
     * How do I file a telephone-related complaint with the FCC?
     * Does the FCC regulate all telephone issues?


   Skip Television FAQ Links Television
     * How can I file a complaint about obscenity on the radio or
       television?
     * Is there a petition pending with the FCC to do away with religious
       programming?
     * What can I do about interference on my television?


   Skip Radio FAQ Links Radio
     * How can I file a complaint about obscenity on the radio or
       television?
     * How can I start my own radio station?
     * What can I do about interference to my radio?


   Skip Cabel FAQ Links Cable
     * How can I file a complaint against my cable company?
     * Who decides on programs and changes in programming?


   Skip Internet FAQ Links Internet
     * How do I file a complaint against my Internet Service Provider?
     * I have been connected to a web site and now I am being charged for
       international calls on my telephone bill. How do I file a
       complaint?


   Skip sateilite FAQ Links Satellite
     * Can I place my satellite dish anywhere on my property?
     * What is the Satellite Home Viewer Improvement Act of 1999?
     * How does SHVIA affect the programming that is available to persons
       who subscribe to satellite TV service?
     * Must a satellite company provide local channels to any subscriber
       who wants the channels?
     * Where can I obtain more information on SHVIA?

